DOC fix intercept_ and coef_ docs for LogisticRegression(CV) (#7420)

* coef_ can be of shape (1, n_features) for binary problems;
* intercept can be of shape (1,) for binary problems;
* intercept_ is set to zero, not unavailable when fit_intercept is False;
* raw_coef_ is removed (see GH-3416)

